{"tid":1813870,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無試過比好熟嘅舊朋友unfol?","createTime":"2020-01-06T14:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T07:23:34.000Z","uid":200604,"like":21,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"57df484b8a00adf836641bc504b43f522e62d4bc","tid":1813870,"uid":200604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"或者成長嘅附屬品就係友情嘅流逝啦<br />\n定女人嘅友情係較為脆弱？<br />\n<br />\n中學grad咗兩年左右 <br />\n無乜點同啲好朋友傾計同約去街 <br />\n有兩個識咗十年以上<br />\n有兩個移咗民唔會再返嚟<br />\n以前糖痴豆到連廁所都一齊去<br />\n<br />\nGrad後我講咗句野 朋友覺得唔啱聽<br />\n之後佢返親母校都係約其他common fd<br />\n但刻意無約我 <br />\n<br />\n然後最近一兩星期發現比佢地unfol咗 <br />\n互相睇唔到對方近況<br />\n因為幾個朋友都係用private ac <br />\n得三十個follower左右<br />\n我諗係覺得我唔再係close friends <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中一個朋友話係自己問題<br />\n唔想睇到人咁開心反映自己生活沉悶<br />\n其他我無問 亦唔敢問<br />\n最近ig唔算活躍 無乜點post野 <br />\n<br />\n請問咁係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我應該接受 定嘗試挽回段關係<br />\n利申黃"},{"pid":"70d4b308aeee1d5946a773b4f1411059e5d40252","tid":1813870,"uid":43041,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:43:21.000Z","msg":"unfol咪unfol<br />\n<br />\n佢又唔係你邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34589619811875ace49bb4572a3cc7a15f4ad06b","tid":1813870,"uid":256620,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"70d4b308aeee1d5946a773b4f1411059e5d40252","tid":1813870,"uid":43041,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:43:21.000Z","msg":"unfol咪unfol<br />\n<br />\n佢又唔係你邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:45:18.000Z","msg":"[行動] 對 抗 濫 捕 對 策 (長文幫手推下)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1813796/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1813796/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"32cad042aff8d99da1d3e962438334eea63780c8","tid":1813870,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime